	<div class="container" align="center">

		<div class="question">
			<h3>Remove the least possible number of dots from the figure so that it will be impossible to form a square with any remaining dots as vertices.
			</h3>
			<h5>[On removing only 10 dots you will complete this level. However, if you remove 11 dots, such that no squares form, and submit, you will get partial points and will procees to the next level.]
			</h5>
		</div>
